{"tid":2489680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大國會視像會議，有議員赤裸入鏡，事後解釋不知鏡頭開啟","createTime":"2021-04-15T05:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T15:16:48.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5a14f38969f7d47f57e44f6b088246c5912c62a1","tid":2489680,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/730748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F730748&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b435400e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F730748&h=45aa3f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/730748</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】加拿大一名下議院議員視像參與國會會議時，赤裸入鏡，他道歉說不知道鏡頭開著了。<br />\n<br />\n魁北克下議員阿莫斯周四視像旁聽議員諮詢環節時，由其他議員提醒「最好穿回衣物」。當時全身赤裸的阿莫斯，事後解釋剛慢跑完、準備更衣，同時旁聽會議，沒留意電腦鏡頭不小心開著了，對事件感抱歉，承諾不會再犯。<br />\n<br />\n阿莫斯這日未獲安排在會上發言，他的畫面只在內部頻道出現，沒有在公眾頻道直播。阿莫斯所屬的自由黨表示接受其解釋，認為阿莫斯是無心之失，議長事後提醒所有議員，在靠近鏡頭和咪高峰時要格外留神。"},{"pid":"c25fa5bc81c6549edef86ffe852fddc78ef97f3a","tid":2489680,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"Zoom strikes again: Canadian parliament can&rsquo;t unsee <strong>member&rsquo;s member</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4478a19d5d0d43274dec21edd00b5e09f76a10e9","tid":2489680,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"有冇流出"}]}